author: Ubisoft
description:
Season 3 introduces a new Dual Front assignment. Take control of the Keres Safe Room and hold your ground while downloading critical data.

Play Operation High Stakes on September 2.

About Rainbow Six Siege X:
Rainbow Six Siege X is an exciting, new approach to the first-person shooter experience that puts tactical combat and masterful destruction at the center of the action. Lead your team of unique operators through tense and thrilling combat scenarios, and achieve victory through smart preparation and strategic improvisation. Rainbow Six Siege X is available now on Xbox, PlayStation® and PC.

#Ubisoft #R6SiegeX

About Ubisoft:
Ubisoft is a creator of worlds, committed to enriching players’ lives with original and memorable entertainment experiences. Ubisoft’s global teams create and develop a deep and diverse portfolio of games, featuring brands such as Assassin’s Creed®, Brawlhalla®, For Honor®, Far Cry®, Tom Clancy’s Ghost Recon®, Just Dance®, Rabbids®, Tom Clancy’s Rainbow Six®
title: Rainbow Six Siege X: Keres Safe Room Trailer
